      </div>
      <div class="col-md-7 wrap-about py-5 pr-md-4 ftco-animate">
        <h2 class="mb-4">Welcome to Salem Bakhit High School</h2>
        <p>
          Established in 2006, <strong>Salem Bakhit High School</strong> has remained a pillar of quality education and holistic student development in our community. We are a forward-thinking academic institution committed to nurturing excellence, building character, and empowering future leaders.
        </p>
        <p>
          At Salem Bakhit, we believe that education is more than just acquiring knowledge — it’s about cultivating curiosity, instilling discipline, and preparing students for lifelong success. We create a safe and supportive environment where every learner is inspired to reach their full potential both inside and outside the classroom.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our dedicated team of qualified educators uses modern teaching methods, enriched curricula, and values-based mentorship to ensure that students not only excel academically but also grow as responsible, morally grounded individuals. From junior to senior levels, we equip our students with the critical thinking skills and leadership mindset needed in today’s dynamic world.
        </p>
        <p>
          Whether you are a parent seeking the best for your child or a student aspiring to be part of a vibrant learning community — we welcome you to the Salem Bakhit family, where every dream is nurtured and every future is bright.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


